    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an unstoppable force and survive endless waves of enemies in this unforgiving action rogue-lite auto-shooter. <br>Unlock new equipment and upgrade your stats to keep pushing the limit of how long you can survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270120/extras/b28089c63f13fc8cf83ff0eebe713d18.poster.avif?t=1770288731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270120/extras/b28089c63f13fc8cf83ff0eebe713d18.webm?t=1770288731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270120/extras/b28089c63f13fc8cf83ff0eebe713d18.mp4?t=1770288731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270120/extras/0d2645d31cedec92bac9c5b6565ae865.webp?t=1770288731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270120/extras_big/0d2645d31cedec92bac9c5b6565ae865.avif?t=1770288731 width=800 height=48 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather valuable resources during your run so that you later can upgrade your permanent stats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat strong units and find blueprints to unlock new equipment for your equipment card rolls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rank up and unlock more options for your loadout such as perks, ultimate abilities and primary weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270120/extras/27825ddbd8f89a516429b2cccf15ccde.webp?t=1770288731\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270120/extras_big/27825ddbd8f89a516429b2cccf15ccde.avif?t=1770288731 width=800 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Prioritize weapon cards during the first waves to stay ahead </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Prioritize picking up experience when planning how to dodge the swarm </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Do as many quests as possible </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Don't get hit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul>",
